      <h2>{{"Adblock Plus for Chrome"|translate("s64")}}</h2>

      <p>
      {{"Are you fed up with advertisers infringing on your browsing experience? Adblock Plus for Chrome blocks annoying, intrusive ads like blinking banners, pop-ups and video commercials on YouTube and Facebook. Want more? You can disable all ads and browse completely ad-free, and activate additional privacy and security features such as tracking and malware protection."|translate("s65")}}
