      {{"Installing Adblock Plus for Chrome only takes a few seconds. Simply click the <strong>Install for Chrome</strong> button above. <strong>Please note</strong>: Chrome displays a warning stating that Adblock Plus can access data on any website you visit. This is a standard warning for Chrome extensions running on every tab. We promise to never collect any data about you."|translate("s66")}}
      </p>

      <p>
      {{"Adblock Plus is the most advanced ad blocker for Chrome. It’s developed by the open source community and free to use. Used on more than 100 million devices, it’s one of the most popular extensions ever."|translate("s67")}}
      </p>
    </div>

    <div id="tab-firefox" class="more-tab">
      <h2>{{"Adblock Plus for Firefox"|translate("s60")}}</h2>

      <p>
      {{"Adblock Plus for Firefox is more than a pop-up blocker. Are banners, overlays and other annoying advertisements ruining your browsing experience? Install Adblock Plus for Firefox and experience the web as it should be. Want more? You can disable all ads and browse completely ad-free, and activate additional privacy and security features such as tracking and malware protection."|translate("abp-firefox-description-p1")}}
      </p>

      <p>
      {{"Installing Adblock Plus for Firefox only takes a few seconds. Simply click the <strong>Install for Firefox</strong> button above. Depending on the filter lists you have activated, you can even block YouTube video ads and block Facebook tracking. Filter lists are created by members of the open source community and free to use. If you don't want to rely on filter lists, you can create your own filter rules to customize your online experience."|translate("abp-firefox-description-p2")}}
      </p>

      <p>
      {{"Adblock Plus for Firefox is the most downloaded browser extension worldwide and winner of the About.com Reader's Choice Award in 2011 and 2013, as well as the Linux New Media award for the Best Open Source Firefox Extension."|translate("s63")}}
      </p>
    </div>

    <div id="tab-internet-explorer" class="more-tab">
      <h2>{{"Adblock Plus for Internet Explorer"|translate("s81")}}</h2>

      <p>
      {{"Developing extensions for Internet Explorer is challenging; that’s one of the reasons there aren’t as many extensions on Internet Explorer as on Firefox, Chrome or Opera. Installing Adblock Plus for Internet Explorer is a little different than on other browsers. Usually, the extension is directly added to the browser; however, for Internet Explorer you need to install it through a so-called setup program. But don’t worry - it takes under 30 seconds to install. Click the <strong>Install for Internet Explorer</strong> button above and start browsing in peace."|translate("s83")}}
